PSA: (cross posted here: https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1719271430728629)
If you run into this error, try clearing your localStorage - specifically the entry that ends in `_AIHUB_RECENTS`. This can affect anyone who made edits to projects, conversations, app runs, or chatbots between the middle of last week to yesterday.
